data.description: Large beautiful, two-story home located in Lumberton off West Walton! Fabulous 1.5 acres down a quiet dead-end road. Four bedrooms and two bathrooms upstairs/1/2 down. Incredible Kitchen has been renovated with lots of fresh updates throughout including a coffee bar and wine fridge! The formal living room and master bedroom both have brick fireplaces. A separate dining makes a great space for entertaining. This home is perfect for gatherings with lots of parking and room for guests including the balcony. The in-ground pool is surrounded with pink azaleas during the Spring and black iron fencing. Carport to keep your boat covered. There is so much storage including the floored attic running the length of the home. If you're in the market for some peaceful property with room to move and a pool to relax, check this one out.
